<p>After countless meetings and discussions with the co-founder Chris Shortt, a decision was made to take a metro-like look for the website, keeping things as minimalist as possible. The entire project took about two month from start to finish, and is still ongoing. As the company goes from strength to strength they will be looking to showcase their projects and latest developments. The website makes uses of the latest in web technologies, including CSS3 and HTML elements.</p>
